            <div type="e">
                <column>01</column>
                <head>War, the Chastisement of Nations</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>With war now breaking out in Austria, Prussia, Italy, Spain and South
                    America, the editor offers the South as an example "for the admiration of the
                    world" since "there is no nobler spectacle than that of a conquered people
                    preserving their honor, self-respect and christian virtues."</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
